Third-Party Acknowledgments

Sky and Sea Alert is an independent, open-source MeshMonitor Auto Responder script designed to integrate with:

- MeshMonitor (by Yeraze)  
- Meshtastic (open-source LoRa mesh networking platform)  
- Local ADS-B software such as dump1090 and readsb  
- Local AIS software such as AIS-catcher and rtl_ais  
- ADS-B Exchange API Lite (via RapidAPI)  
- AIS Hub API (https://www.aishub.net/api)

This project may use locally collected ADS-B and AIS data or official cloud APIs provided by third parties. It does not scrape websites, rebroadcast proprietary feeds, or distribute shared API credentials.

All trademarks, logos, and brand names are the property of their respective owners.  
Sky and Sea Alert is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially connected to MeshMonitor, Meshtastic, ADS-B Exchange, AIS Hub, RapidAPI, or any other referenced platform, provider, or organization.
